聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如我地唔打好 我地好難用<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最低程度既損傷</span><br />\n去真正<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 奪權當家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n前一兩日李柱銘俾狗塔，但喺美國政壇引起如此大既迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。正係<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為先前聯署同請求美帝落實《人權及民主法案》而致</span>，趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\">俾藉口美帝加速打殘狗共</span>，何樂不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n1.你話，小，我光復香港既目標都唔同~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答：但你咁樣係可以<span style=\"color: teal;\">幫到國際戰線+其他戰線既手足wo，兄弟爬山可以共同努力㗎，你幫我，我幫你咁解姐</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.你又話，小，會曬我時間㗎，我時間好寶貴㗎~<br />\n答：去vote4 hk 簽署到confirm signature<span style=\"color: gold;\">【記得一定要出Your signature has been confirmed個畫面你先簽到聯署㗎】，唔夠1分鐘，<span style=\"color: teal;\">幾個聯署咪最多曬你十分鐘左右</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n黃色Youtuber圈都話要CLS【其實應該再多個 No Skip既，因為咁樣可以令果個Youtuber收到錢錢，咪做到更加多高質既片俾你地咯~】<br />\n</span><br />\n聯署都可以嚟個<span style=\"color: teal;\">SECS</span>㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">S: Sign【簽署聯署】<br />\nE: Email【去Email度Click封聯署確認信】<br />\nC: Confirm【確認有綠色提示字】<br />\nS: Share【俾更多人一齊簽，眾志成城】<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3.你又話，小，我一個簽又無人簽，玩撚啊？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答: 恭喜你答到問題所在啦~ 你一個簽係唔夠㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以要<span style=\"color: gold;\">些牙</span>，同<span style=\"color: gold;\">玩個聯署challenge，邊個簽咗一個聯署就Tag三個人，而果三個人亦要接受挑戰，自己簽完一個聯署再tag三個人</span>，如此類推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<span style=\"color: orange;\">616都做到200萬人</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">69都做到100萬人啦</span>，聯署要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10萬</span></span>咋wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，成10倍既容錯率，點計我地都著數啦~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">香港人最鍾意跣人蕉皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你咪可以喺幫到運動既同時合法地跣一鑊，對方又唔會話你撚化佢既，搞掂~</span><br />\n<br />\n4.你又話，小，我憎鳩外國勢力㗎【同時適合於政治潔癖】<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答：其實呢，就同你<span style=\"color: gold;\">憎鳩飯民</span>既道理一樣【我都係憎鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />】，你憎鳩咪<span style=\"color: teal;\">利用佢最大功用</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: teal;\">用完咪當佢condom咯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: red;\">飯民點解可以隨時當你condom</span>，咪就<span style=\"color: teal;\">因為佢喺需要既位度利用到你既最大功用</span>，用完咁咪搞掂當condom咯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。同樣地，你憎鳩外國勢力，就要利用外國勢力對你既最大公倍數嚟達成你既目標。大家既目標都係要<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，實現雙普選㗎</span>，再經<span style=\"color: teal;\">民選政府</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">實現五大訴求</span>㗎係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢話就唔多講啦，<span style=\"color: gold;\">連結就喺上面~記得些牙，簽曬佢啊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">國族自主自強，構築香港共同體<br />\n重新立約，還我民主<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路<br />\n</span></span><br />\nP.S. 約 = 社會契約論，有興趣自己google~"},{"pid":"ff36f40c7ed445feba61eb3ae2233f7187e9b7e1","tid":1981212,"uid":133763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:08:07.000Z","msg":"今日電子妓女<br />\n他日電子拍拖"}]}